                 <div class="col-md-12">
                 <div class="row">
                 <center>
                 <!--paragraph 1-->
                 <div class="section__title">Transform Your Business. <br/> Become A Rubrik Partner.</div>
                  <div class="section_paragraph">We’re disrupting a $48 billion backup and recovery market with a 100% channel-focused business model. </div>
                  </center>
