                 <center> 
                 <div class="section__paragraph_small">Any partner interested in joining the Rubrik Partner Program but resides outside US, Canada, or EMEA, please send an email to <a href="mailto:goforward@rubrik.com">goforward@rubrik.com</a> to get further information.
                 </div>
                 
                 <h6 style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">
                 By completing and submitting this Online Company Application (“Application”), Company promises Rubrik: All the following information is accurate, complete and current. Company will notify Rubrik promptly of all changes. The person(s) completing this Application and accepting the Terms is authorized by the Company to do so. Once Rubrik accepts Company’s Application, the Company acknowledges and agrees it is bound by the Terms, and, if Company does not agree to all of these Terms, do not proceed to complete this Application and accept the Terms.
                 </h6>
                 <br/>
                 </center>
